ivardefs.name: about_
ivardefs.desc: Other resources that pertain to this communication and to which this communication should be associated.

ivardefs.name: basedOn_
ivardefs.desc: An order, proposal or plan fulfilled in whole or in part by this Communication.

ivardefs.name: category_
ivardefs.desc: The type of message conveyed such as alert, notification, reminder, instruction, etc.

ivardefs.name: encounter
ivardefs.desc: The Encounter during which this Communication was created or to which the creation of this record is tightly associated.

ivardefs.name: identifier_
ivardefs.desc: Business identifiers assigned to this communication by the performer or other systems which remain constant as the resource is updated and propagates from server to server.

ivardefs.name: inResponseTo_
ivardefs.desc: Prior communication that this communication is in response to.

ivardefs.name: instantiatesCanonical_
ivardefs.desc: The URL pointing to a FHIR-defined protocol, guideline, orderset or other definition that is adhered to in whole or in part by this Communication.

ivardefs.name: instantiatesUri_
ivardefs.desc: The URL pointing to an externally maintained protocol, guideline, orderset or other definition that is adhered to in whole or in part by this Communication.

ivardefs.name: medium_
ivardefs.desc: A channel that was used for this communication (e.g. email, fax).

ivardefs.name: note_
ivardefs.desc: Additional notes or commentary about the communication by the sender, receiver or other interested parties.

ivardefs.name: partOf_
ivardefs.desc: A larger event (e.g. Communication, Procedure) of which this particular communication is a component or step.

ivardefs.name: payload_
ivardefs.desc: Text, attachment(s), or resource(s) that was communicated to the recipient.

ivardefs.name: priority
ivardefs.desc: Characterizes how quickly the planned or in progress communication must be addressed. Includes concepts such as stat, urgent, routine.

ivardefs.name: reasonCode_
ivardefs.desc: The reason or justification for the communication.

ivardefs.name: reasonReference_
ivardefs.desc: Indicates another resource whose existence justifies this communication.

ivardefs.name: received
ivardefs.desc: The time when this communication arrived at the destination.

ivardefs.name: recipient_
ivardefs.desc: The entity (e.g. person, organization, clinical information system, care team or device) which is the target of the communication.

ivardefs.name: sender
ivardefs.desc: The entity (e.g. person, organization, clinical information system, or device) which is the source of the communication.

ivardefs.name: sent
ivardefs.desc: The time when this communication was sent.

ivardefs.name: status
ivardefs.desc: The status of the transmission.

ivardefs.name: statusReason
ivardefs.desc: Captures the reason for the current state of the Communication.

ivardefs.name: subject
ivardefs.desc: The patient or group that was the focus of this communication.

ivardefs.name: topic
ivardefs.desc: Description of the purpose/content, similar to a subject line in an email.

properties.desc: An occurrence of information being transmitted; e.g. an alert that was sent to a responsible provider, a public health agency communication to a provider/reporter in response to a case report for a reportable condition.
